e Web APIs and Background Services using .NET Core and C#.</li>\n  <li>Deployed microservices using Docker, Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS), and Azure Web Apps.</li>\n  <li>Built responsive UIs using <strong>Angular</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Integrated observability tools including Azure Monitor, Application Insights, and Seq logs.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Project:</strong> NRS (Qterics Device Management Platform)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Reverse engineered and successfully compiled a legacy device management platform,</strong> enabling direct maintenance and issue resolution.</li>\n  <li>Developed and supported applications using <strong>C#, .NET Framework, ASP .NET, WCF SOAP Services, and MySQL</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Built and tested SOAP integrations using <strong>SOAP UI</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Managed deployments on <strong>AWS EC2 Windows</strong>, <strong>Auto Scaling Groups (ASG)</strong>, and <strong>AWS CodePipeline</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Monitored production environments using <strong>Amazon CloudWatch</strong> and resolved critical production issues.</li>\n</ul>","resumeId":24253312,"position":1,"isMonthUntilHidden":false,"isDateUntilPresent":true,"isMonthFromHidden":false,"normalizedJobTitleId":null,"reasonForResignation":null,"plannedResignationDate":null,"duration":47,"department":null,"employmentType":null,"employerProfilesAttributes":{"id":25743989,"businessType":null,"foundationYear":null,"capital":null,"sales":null,"noOfEmployee":null,"stockListing":null,"resumeWorkExperienceId":44348102,"position":null},"cid":null},{"id":44347961,"title":"Senior Software Developer","employer":"Globals ITeS","city":"Bengaluru","dateFrom":"2016-06-01","dateUntil":"2018-11-01","description":"<p><strong>Project:</strong> Educube ERP – a cloud-based SaaS solution for educational institutions.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Contributed to Educube 3.0 development with MVC, C#, AJAX, and Bootstrap.</li>\n  <li>Designed SQL Server databases and implemented complex store